des:
ECCOTEMP products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your water heater.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your water heater - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your ECCOTEMP products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "ECCOTEMP" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one tuya account in our "ECCOTEMP" app;
(3). You need to have some ECCOTEMP devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "ECCOTEMP" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Eccotemp" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Eccotemp" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Eccotemp ", and you'll be navigated to ECCOTEMP login page;
(9). Input your ECCOTEMP account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on water heater.”
“Alexa, turn off water heater.”
“Alexa, set water heater to 60 degrees.”
